\c 23
\s UJoshuwa ulaya abantu ukuthi bathembeke
\p
\v 1 Kwasekusithi emva kwensuku ezinengi emva kokuthi iN\nd kosi\nd* isimphumuzile\x + 21.44; 22.4.\x* uIsrayeli ezitheni zonke zabo inhlangothi zonke, loJoshuwa wayesemdala\x + 13.1.\x* elensuku ezinengi,
\v 2 uJoshuwa wabiza uIsrayeli wonke\x + 24.1. Dute. 31.28. 1 Lan. 28.1.\x*, abadala babo, lenhloko zabo, labahluleli babo, lenduna zabo\x + 1.10.\x*, wathi kubo: Mina sengimdala ngilensuku ezinengi.
\v 3 Lina selibonile konke iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu ekwenzileyo kulezizizwe zonke ngenxa yenu, ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu yiyo elilweleyo\x + Eks. 14.14.\x*.
\v 4 Bonani, ngilabele ngenkatho\x + 13.6.\x* lezizizwe eziseleyo zibe yilifa lezizwe zenu, kusukela eJordani, lazo zonke izizwe engiziqumileyo, ngitsho kuze kube selwandle olukhulu \x + 15.12.\x*lapho okutshona khona ilanga.
\v 5 IN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu izazixotsha-ke\x + Eks. 23.30; 33.2; 34.11. Dute. 4.38; 11.23. Josh. 13.6.\x* phambi kwenu, izixotshe elifeni phambi kwenu, njalo lizakudla ilifa lelizwe, njengalokho iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu ikhulumile kini\x + Nani 33.53.\x*.
\v 6 Ngakho qinani kakhulu ukugcina lokwenza konke okubhaliweyo egwalweni lomlayo kaMozisi\x + 1.7.\x*, ukuze lingaphambuki kuwo liye ngakwesokunene loba ngakwesokhohlo\x + Dute. 5.32.\x*,
\v 7 ukuze lingangeni kulezi izizwe\x + Eks. 23.33. Dute. 7.2,3.\x*, lezi ezisele lani, lingaphathi ibizo labonkulunkulu bazo\x + Eks. 23.13. Hlab. 16.4.\x*, lingafungisi \add ngabo\x + Jer. 5.7. Zef. 1.5.\x*\add*, lingabakhonzi, lingakhothami kubo,
\v 8 kodwa linamathele\x + 22.5. Dute. 10.20.\x* eN\nd kosi\nd*ni uNkulunkulu wenu njengoba lenzile kuze kube lamuhla.
\v 9 Ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* ixotshile elifeni phambi kwenu izizwe ezinkulu lezilamandla\x + Dute. 11.23.\x*; lina-ke kakulamuntu ome phambi kwenu\x + 10.8; 21.44.\x* kuze kube lamuhla.
\v 10 Umuntu oyedwa kini uzaxotsha inkulungwane\x + Levi 26.8. Hlu. 3.31; 15.15. 2 Sam. 23.8.\x*, ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu yiyo elilwelayo, njengalokho ikhulumile kini\x + 23.3.\x*.
\v 11 Ngakho ziqaphelisiseni\x + 22.5.\x* ukuthanda iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu.
\v 12 Ngoba uba libuyela lokubuyela\x + 23.3.\x*, linamathele kunsali yalezizizwe, lezi ezisele lani, lithathane lazo\x + Eks.34.16.\x*, lingene kuzo, lazo kini,
\v 13 yazini lokwazi ukuthi iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu kayiyikuqhubeka ngokuzixotsha elifeni lezizizwe phambi kwenu\x + Hlu. 2.3,21. Josh. 13.6.\x*; kodwa zizakuba yisifu lomjibila kini\x + Nani 33.55. Hlu. 2.3. Eks. 23.33. 1 Kho. 11.4.\x*, zibe luswazi enhlangothini zenu, lameva emehlweni enu, lize libhubhe liphele kulelilizwe elihle, iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu elinike lona.
\v 14 Khangelani-ke, ngihamba lamuhla ngendlela yomhlaba wonke\x + 1 Kho. 2.2.\x*. Njalo liyazi enhliziyweni yenu yonke lemphefumulweni wenu wonke ukuthi akukho lelizwi elilodwa elehlulekayo kuwo wonke amazwi amahle iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu ewakhulumileyo phezu kwenu\x + 21.45.\x*; wonke ezile kini, akukho lelizwi elilodwa elehlulekayo kuwo.
\v 15 Kuzakuthi-ke, njengalokhu zonke izinto ezinhle iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu eyazikhuluma kini sezilehlele, ngokunjalo iN\nd kosi\nd* izalehlisela zonke izinto ezimbi\x + Levi 26.14. Dute. 28.15,16,63.\x*, ize ilibhubhise liphele kulelilizwe elihle iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu elinike lona.
\v 16 Uba liseqa isivumelwano\x + Dute. 17.2.\x* seN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu eyalilaya sona, lisuke liyekhonza abanye onkulunkulu, likhothame kibo, khona ulaka lweN\nd kosi\nd* luzalivuthela, libhubhe masinyane liphele kulelilizwe elihle elinike lona.